<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The videoWidget() property of <db:link xlink:href="qvideowidgetcontrol.xml">QVideoWidgetControl</db:link> provides a pointer to a video widget implemented by the control's media service. This widget is owned by the media service and so care should be taken not to delete it.</db:para>
<db:programlisting language="cpp">QVideoWidgetControl *widgetControl = mediaService-&gt;requestControl&lt;QVideoWidgetControl *&gt;();
layout-&gt;addWidget(widgetControl-&gt;videoWidget());
</db:programlisting>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qvideowidgetcontrol.xml">QVideoWidgetControl</db:link> is one of number of possible video output controls.</db:para>
<db:para>The interface name of <db:link xlink:href="qvideowidgetcontrol.xml">QVideoWidgetControl</db:link> is <db:code>org.qt-project.qt.videowidgetcontrol/5.0</db:code> as defined in <db:link xlink:href="qvideowidgetcontrol.xml#QVideoWidgetControl_iid">QVideoWidgetControl_iid</db:link>.</db:para>
